com.xiantrimble.combinatorics
Interface CombinatoricEngine<T>

Type Parameters:
T - the type of the elements being combined or permuted.
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractCombinatoricEngine, CombinationsEngine, IndexBasedPermutationsEngine, PermutationsEngine
public interface CombinatoricEngine<T>

Combinatoric engines provide access to the state changes that are happening while generating combinations and permutations. Although this package does not provide minimal change ordering, it does try to reduce state change to improve performance. Implementations of this class give you access to that information.

Author:
Christian Trimble
